<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #1d4ed8); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .footer { background: #1e293b; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; }
        .button { background: #10b981; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block; margin: 15px 0; }
        .info-box { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; }
        .status-badge { background: #fbbf24; color: #92400e; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 16px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🏢 IGL AMC Dashboard</h1>
            <h2>Registration Submitted Successfully</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h3>Hello {{userName}},</h3>
            <p>Thank you for submitting your registration for <strong>{{userRole}}</strong> access to the IGL AMC Dashboard.</p>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <h4>📋 Registration Details</h4>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
                    <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{userName}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Role:</strong> {{userRole}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Employee ID:</strong> {{empId}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Submission Date:</strong> {{submissionDate}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status-badge">Pending Approval</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h4>🔄 What Happens Next?</h4>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Admin Review:</strong> Your request is now pending admin approval</li>
                <li><strong>Timeline:</strong> Admin will review within 24-48 hours</li>
                <li><strong>Notification:</strong> You'll receive an email once approved</li>
                <li><strong>Access:</strong> After approval, you can login to the dashboard</li>
            </ol>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Visit Dashboard</a>
            </div>

            <p><em>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</em></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2025 IGL AMC Dashboard. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
